---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
	<main>
    <h1>Hai, gue Zul.</h1>
    <p><em>Professional Procrastinator who somehow builds data things.</em></p>
    <p>Udah nyentuh banyak hal di dunia kerja — finance, IT, data ops. Masih penasaran sama banyak hal lainnya.</p>
    <p>Nulis di sini buat diri sendiri sebenernya. Semacam catatan harian yang dipublish — soal data, teknis, random, dan kadang terlalu jujur.</p>
    <p>Kalau lo nyasar ke sini, enjoy.</p>
</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
